<td class="session-details-drawer" colspan="4"><div class="well-session-details span5" id="session-details-21848"><p>July 10th 1944- Intelligence has found  Capt. John Lucas at Stalag Luft 1 in northern Germany.  Your mission is to parachute in rescue Capt. Lucas and transport him back to safety.  Even with Super Powers this mission will be a challenge for Talent Operations Group 3.</p>
