<tr id="session-22374"><td class="slot-period-empty"><span class="slot-period">6-10pm</span></td><td><strong> Friday Knight - Scion RPG</strong></td><td>&mdash;</td></tr>
<tr><td class="session-details-drawer"></td>
<td class="session-details-drawer" colspan="4"><div class="well-session-details span5" id="session-details-22374"><p>Normally, new Scions become aware of their divine parentage when their immortal parent performs a Visitation. With the escalation of the Titanwar, Ares, God of War, just can’t clear his schedule, and he’s overdue to see his newest child. Normally, relatively young Scions wouldn’t be asked to perform a first contact, but this is a family matter, and you are family…
</p>
</div></td></tr>
